title: java文件夹中无server
author: Nine_Sang
txt_content:
日志：
Error: missing `server' JVM at `C:\Program Files (x86)\Java\jre1.8.0_251\bin\server\jvm.dll'.
Please install or use the JRE or JDK that contains these missing components.
bat：
SET Money=2024M

SET Server=spigot-1.16.1.jar

SET SetCanShu=-XX:+UseG1GC -server -XX:+UseFastAccessorMethods -XX:+OptimizeStringConcat -XX:+AggressiveOpts -XX:MaxGCPauseMillis=10 -XX:+UseStringDeduplication

java -Xms128M -Xmx%Money% %SetCanShu% -jar %Server% nogui

replies.author: 蕾米洛伊
replies.txt_content:

*** Please download a new build ...
这不是正常开了吗，一开始卡了20秒是因为你下载的构建版本不是最新的，为了提醒你更新所以才会延迟20秒启动233

SET Server=spigot-1.16.1.jar
